pageContext.claim: “You will never hear this on the Fake News concerning the China Virus, but by comparison to most other countries, who are suffering greatly, we are doing very well - and we have done things that few other countries could have done!”
pageContext.analysis: The United States continues to lead the world in overall coronavirus deaths and cases. When considering the number of people who have died or contracted covid-19 per 100,000 , it continues to be in the top 20 countries.
